Initial commit: Chess Overlay Android app structure

- Complete Android project with floating overlay functionality
- MainActivity with permission handling and service management
- OverlayService for floating button and chess analysis
- ChessAnalyzer for coordinating screen capture and analysis
- ChessBoardDetector using OpenCV for board recognition
- StockfishEngine integration for move analysis
- Arabic UI support and comprehensive documentation
- OpenCV module structure with basic classes
- All necessary Android resources and configurations

